This pull has been inactive for almost 6 months. 
Would be great if someone picked this up, but as there isn't enough confidence in this implementation as-is, and thus it won't merged in this state, I'm closing the pull.
@ashleyholman let me know if you intend to work on this again, I'll reopen.
